#: ../../source/api/Backtest.rst:2
msgid "Backtester 策略回测器"
msgstr "Backtester strategy backtesting engine"

#: ../../source/api/Backtest.rst:4
msgid "Backtester类用于对operator对象进行回测操作。"
msgstr "The Backtester class is used to backtest operator objects."

#: ../../source/api/Backtest.rst:6
msgid ""
"本类的属性包括回测计算中所需的所有参数，包括回测过程中产生的结果数据，这"
"些结果数据以ndarray的形式 在对象的生命周期内长期保存，并可以反复刷新。"
msgstr ""
"This class’s attributes include all parameters required for backtest "
"calculations, as well as the result data generated during the backtest. "
"These result data are stored as ndarrays and retained for the lifetime "
"of the object, and can be refreshed repeatedly."

#: ../../source/api/Backtest.rst:9 of qteasy.backtest.Backtester:5
msgid ""
"这个类只有在operator对象被创建之后才能被实例化，因为Backtester类需要依赖"
"operator对象来生成交易 信号和执行交易。典型用法如下："
msgstr ""
"This class can only be instantiated after the operator object has been "
"created, because the Backtester class depends on the operator object to "
"generate trading signals and execute trades. Typical usage is as follows:"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester:1
msgid ""
"Backtester类用于对operator对象进行回测操作。 本类的属性包括回测计算中所需"
"的所有参数，包括回测过程中产生的结果数据，这些结果数据以ndarray的形式 在"
"对象的生命周期内长期保存，并可以反复刷新。"
msgstr ""
"The Backtester class is used to backtest an operator object. This "
"class’s attributes include all parameters required for backtest "
"calculations, as well as the result data generated during the backtest. "
"These result data are stored as ndarrays and retained for the lifetime "
"of the object, and can be refreshed repeatedly."

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester:23
msgid "交易操作对象，包含交易信号生成和交易执行的逻辑"
msgstr ""
"A trading operation object that includes the logic for generating "
"trading signals and executing trades"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester
msgid "type"
msgstr "type"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester:25
msgid "Operator"
msgstr "Operator"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.clear_backtest_buffers:1
msgid ""
"清除回测结果缓存数据，将回测结果数据重置为空数组，以便重新进行回测计算"
msgstr ""
"Clear the cached backtest results data and reset the backtest results "
"data to an empty array so that the backtest can be recalculated."

#: ../../source/api/Backtest.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr "Return type"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.evaluate_result:1
msgid "生成交易结果的评价报告，保存在self.evaluate_result属性中"
msgstr ""
"Generates an evaluation report of the trading results and saves it in "
"the self.evaluate_result attribute"

#: ../../source/api/Backtest.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr "parameter"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.evaluate_result:3
msgid "回测结果评价指标，详情参见qteasy.evaluate.evaluate()函数"
msgstr ""
"Backtest result evaluation metrics; see the qteasy.evaluate.evaluate() "
"function for details"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.generate_trade_logs:1
msgid ""
"根据回测结果生成交易日志，交易日志是一份完整的交易记录文件，包含每一个交"
"易期间的下列信息。"
msgstr ""
"Generate a trading log based on the backtest results. The trading log is "
"a complete trade record file that contains the following information for "
"each trading period."

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.generate_trade_logs:3
msgid "每一个交易期间包含 8 行数据，分别为："
msgstr "Each trading period contains 8 rows of data, as follows:"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.generate_trade_logs:5
msgid "``0, trade signal``：每一支股票的当期交易信号"
msgstr ""
"``0, trade signal``: the current-period trading signal for each stock"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.generate_trade_logs:6
msgid "``1, price``：每一支股票的当期交易价格"
msgstr "``1, price``: the current-period trading price for each stock"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.generate_trade_logs:7
msgid "``2, traded amounts``：每一支股票的当期交易数量，如果没有交易则为 0"
msgstr ""
"``2, traded amounts``: the current-period traded quantity for each "
"stock; 0 if there is no trade"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.generate_trade_logs:8
msgid ""
"``3, cash changed``：每一支股票的当期现金变动金额，买入为负数，卖出为正数"
msgstr ""
"``3, cash changed``: the current-period cash change amount for each "
"stock; negative for buys and positive for sells"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.generate_trade_logs:9
msgid "``4, trade cost``：每一支股票的当期交易费用"
msgstr "``4, trade cost``: the current-period trading cost for each stock"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.generate_trade_logs:10
msgid "``5, own amounts``：每一支股票的当期末持有数量"
msgstr ""
"``5, own amounts``: the end-of-period holdings quantity for each stock"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.generate_trade_logs:11
msgid "``6, available amounts``：每一支股票的当期末可用数量"
msgstr ""
"``6, available amounts``: the end-of-period available quantity for each "
"stock"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.generate_trade_logs:12
msgid ""
"``7, summary``：当期每一支股票的持仓价值，同时包含汇总数据（当期末持有现"
"金、可用现金、总资产价值）"
msgstr ""
"``7, summary``: the position value of each stock for the current period, "
"also including summary data (cash held at the end of the current period, "
"available cash, total asset value)"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.generate_trade_logs:14
msgid ""
"以上信息以 DataFrame 形式保存，行索引为多级索引，第一/二层为时间/策略组索"
"引，第三层为上述 8 个数据类别。 交易日志文件可以被保存为 csv 格式，文件名"
"为 ``trade_log.csv``。"
msgstr ""
"The above information is saved in the form of a DataFrame. The row index "
"is a MultiIndex: the first/second levels are the time/strategy group "
"indices, and the third level is the 8 data categories above. The trade "
"log file can be saved in CSV format with the filename ``trade_log.csv``."

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.generate_trade_logs:17
msgid "如果提供了文件路径，则将交易日志保存为CSV文件，默认值为None"
msgstr ""
"If a file path is provided, save the trade log as a CSV file; the "
"default is None."

#: ../../source/api/Backtest.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr "Back"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.generate_trade_logs:20
msgid "**trade_log** -- 交易模拟结果数据"
msgstr "**trade_log** -- trade simulation result data"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.generate_trade_summary:1
msgid ""
"生成 trade summary 交易摘要表 (一个更加紧凑的交易汇总表，包含每次交易的关"
"键信息， 以一种更加易于人类阅读的方式呈现，并过滤掉无交易的记录)，函数的"
"输入trade_log_df是函数 generate_trade_logs()的返回值。"
msgstr ""
"Generate the trade summary table (a more compact trade summary table "
"that contains the key information for each trade, presented in a more "
"human-readable way, and filters out records with no trades). The "
"function input trade_log_df is the return value of the function "
"generate_trade_logs()."

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.generate_trade_summary:5
msgid "交易标的名称列表, 如果为None，则使用“N/A”作为名称"
msgstr "List of trading instrument names; if None, use “N/A” as the name."

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.generate_trade_summary:7
msgid ""
"如果提供了文件路径，则将交易摘要表保存为CSV文件，默认值为None，不保存文件"
msgstr ""
"If a file path is provided, save the trade summary table as a CSV file; "
"the default is None (do not save a file)."

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.plot_result:1
msgid "以图表形式生成交易结果"
msgstr "Generate trading results in chart form"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.plot_result:3
msgid "图表的标题名称"
msgstr "The chart title"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.plot_result:5
msgid ""
"是否显示持股仓位区间信息，如果设置为True，则在收益率曲线图上 以红色/绿色"
"条带显示区间的持仓类型（绿色表示持多仓，红色表示持 空仓）颜色越深持仓比例"
"越高"
msgstr ""
"Whether to display position interval information. If set to True, show "
"the position type for each interval on the return curve chart as red/"
"green bands (green indicates holding a long position, red indicates "
"holding a short position). The darker the color, the higher the position "
"ratio."

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.plot_result:9
msgid ""
"是否在收益率曲线图上显示买卖点，如果设置为True，则在收益率曲 线图上以红绿"
"色小箭头标示出买卖点"
msgstr ""
"Whether to show buy/sell points on the return curve chart. If set to "
"True, buy/sell points are marked on the return curve chart with small "
"red/green arrows"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.report_result:1
msgid "生成回测结果的明细报告，报告为纯文本格式，可以使用print命令打印"
msgstr ""
"Generate a detailed report of the backtest results. The report is in "
"plain-text format and can be printed using the print command"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.report_result:3
msgid ""
"交易日志文件的存储路径，默认值为None，如果给出该路径，则在报告中打印交易"
"日志的存储路径"
msgstr ""
"Storage path for the trade log file. The default is None. If this path "
"is provided, the storage path of the trade log is printed in the report"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.report_result:5
msgid ""
"交易汇总记录文件的存储路径，默认值为None，如果给出，则在报告中打印交易汇"
"总记录的存储路径"
msgstr ""
"Storage path for the trade summary record file. The default is None. If "
"provided, print the storage path of the trade summary record in the "
"report."

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.report_result:8
msgid "**report_str** -- 以打印格式排版的回测结果报告"
msgstr "**report_str** -- Backtest results report formatted for printing"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.run:1
msgid "执行回测计算，生成回测结果数据并存入对象属性中"
msgstr ""
"Run the backtest calculations, generate the backtest result data, and "
"store it in the object’s attributes"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.save_complete_values:1
msgid ""
"将 complete_values 保存为 CSV 文件（当 trade_log=True 时由 qt_operator 调"
"用）"
msgstr ""
"Save complete_values as a CSV file (called by qt_operator when "
"trade_log=True)"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.save_complete_values:3
msgid "保存路径，若为 None 则不写入"
msgstr "Save path; if None, nothing is written"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.save_complete_values:6
msgid "成功时返回保存路径，否则返回 None"
msgstr "Return the save path on success; otherwise return None"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.trace_result_df:1
msgid "根据回测结果生成交易过程记录，输出内容为DataFrame格式"
msgstr ""
"Generate a record of the trading process based on the backtest results; "
"the output is in DataFrame format"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.trace_result_df:3
msgid ""
"trace 行与 op_signal_index 的对齐由 Operator 在写入时保证"
"（update_trace_step 使用 全局 signal 行号），此处仅按策略 concat 后设置 "
"index 为 op_signal_index。"
msgstr ""
"Alignment between trace rows and op_signal_index is ensured by the "
"Operator when writing (update_trace_step uses the global signal row "
"number). Here we only concat by strategy and then set the index to "
"op_signal_index."

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.trace_result_df:6
msgid "**trade_trace** -- 交易模拟过程数据"
msgstr "**trade_trace** -- trade simulation process data"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.trade_result_df:1
msgid "根据回测结果生成资产价值记录，输出内容为DataFrame格式"
msgstr ""
"Generate asset value records based on the backtest results; the output "
"is in DataFrame format."

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.trade_result_df:3
msgid "**value_history** -- 交易模拟结果数据"
msgstr "**value_history** -- trade simulation result data"

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.trade_result_final_value:1
msgid "直接快速计算返回回测的终值结果"
msgstr ""
"Directly and quickly compute and return the final value result of the "
"backtest."

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.trade_result_max_drawdown:1
msgid "直接快速计算返回回测的最大回撤结果"
msgstr ""
"Directly and quickly compute and return the maximum drawdown result of "
"the backtest."

#: of qteasy.backtest.Backtester.trade_result_volatility:1
msgid "直接快速计算返回回测的波动率结果"
msgstr ""
"Directly and quickly compute and return the volatility result of the "
"backtest."
